Eventos de Componets

Tema: {{ event.Theme }}

Local: {{ event.Local }}

import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-events', templateUrl: './events.component.html', styleUrls: ['./events.component.scss'], }) export class EventsComponent { public events: any; getEvents(); public getEvents(): void { this.events = [ { Theme: 'Angular 15', Local: 'Salvador', }, { Theme: '.NET', Local: 'São Paulo', }, { Theme: 'Angular e suas novidades', Local: 'Belo Horizonte', }, ]; } }
